Package hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen

Class StmtBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen.StmtBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
StmtListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class StmtBaseListener extends Object implements StmtListener
This class provides an empty implementation of StmtListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
